### SimpleShop API - Product Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT LISTING AND SEARCH
### ==========================================

### Get All Products (now includes images and primaryImage)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products

### Get All Products with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?page=1&limit=2

### Get All Products with Search
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?search=Sample

### Get Products by Category ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?categoryId=1

### Get Products by Category Slug
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?categorySlug=electronics

### Get Products with Price Range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?minPrice=10&maxPrice=100

### Get Products with Multiple Filters
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products?categoryId=1&minPrice=20&maxPrice=50&search=Sample

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT DETAILS
### ==========================================

### Get Product by ID (now includes images array and primaryImage)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1

### Get Product by ID (Non-existent)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/999

### Get Product by ID (Invalid ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/invalid

### Get Product by ID (Inactive Product - should return 404)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/5

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT IMAGES
### ==========================================

### Get Product Images (Public)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/1/images

### Get Product Images for Non-existent Product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/999/images

### Get Product Images for Inactive Product
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/5/images

### ==========================================
### PRODUCT SUMMARIES
### ==========================================

### Get Product Summaries (for cart/quick view - now includes primaryImage)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/products/summary/list

